      <scopecontent id="aspace_a0e9fa4361005ed824bf7585a0f71ec1">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains various items relating to Lady Emma Hamilton, mistress of the British naval hero Admiral Horatio Nelson. Included are a number of bound volumes of printed and manuscript music, several letters among Lady Hamilton's family members, and reproductions of portraits of Lady Hamilton.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
